:艾格頓於2013年7月底被編劇兼導演[[馬修·范恩|馬修·范恩]]選上<ref name="EgertonCast">{{cite web|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=Matthew Vaughn Eyes Newcomer Taron Egerton for ‘Secret Service’ (EXCLUSIVE)|url=https://variety.com/2013/film/news/matthew-vaughn-eyes-newcomer-taron-egerton-for-secret-service-exclusive-1200568145/|work=''[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]''|date=2013-07-25|accessdate=2018-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628062607/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/matthew-vaughn-eyes-newcomer-taron-egerton-for-secret-service-exclusive-1200568145/|archive-date=2017-06-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。構思初期，范恩就打算找個「讓人跌破眼鏡的人選」，而當時24歲的艾格頓還只是個演藝界新人，從未拍過電影<ref name="I Look 電影雜誌 (2015-02)">{{cite book|title=《I Look 電影雜誌》 |year=2015-02 |publisher=我愛電影事業有限公司 |ISSN=1996-423-4 |location=臺灣 |language=zh-tw}}</ref>{{rp|60}}。范恩看出了艾格頓的才華，「就像之前年僅19歲的新人演員[[珍妮佛·勞倫斯|珍妮佛·勞倫斯]]來為[[魔形女|魔形女]]試鏡那樣，只要鏡頭一對準他，你就知道他有幾把刷子。」<ref name="I Look 電影雜誌 (2015-02)"/>{{rp|60}}艾格頓受到父親影響，從小就是個間諜片迷，因此十分興奮能有這個機會<ref name="I Look 電影雜誌 (2015-02)"/>{{rp|27}}。此前，[[亞倫·強森|亞倫·強森]]曾被劇組找上<ref name="FirthCast">{{cite news |title='The Secret Service': Colin Firth in Talks to Star |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/secret-service-colin-firth-talks-448044 |accessdate=2013-09-15 |newspaper=''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' |date=2013-04-29 |last=Kits |first=Borys |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231040234/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/secret-service-colin-firth-talks-448044 |archive-date=2013-12-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="FirthCast2">{{cite web |last1=Reynolds |first1=SIMON |title=Colin Firth in talks for Matthew Vaughn's 'The Secret Service' |url=https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/a477024/colin-firth-in-talks-for-matthew-vaughns-the-secret-service/ |publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |accessdate=2020-02-11 |date=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930145455/https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/a477024/colin-firth-in-talks-for-matthew-vaughns-the-secret-service/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他因故拒絕<ref name="The Independent">{{cite news|last=Denham|first=Jess|title=Kingsman: The Secret Service trailer released: Colin Firth stars as James Bond-style spy|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/kingsman-the-secret-service-trailer-released-colin-firth-stars-as-james-bond-style-spy-9407411.html|work=''[[獨立報|The Independent]]''|date=2014-05-21|accessdate=2018-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209212422/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/kingsman-the-secret-service-trailer-released-colin-firth-stars-as-james-bond-style-spy-9407411.html|archive-date=2018-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有超過60位男演員為該角試鏡<ref name="I Look 電影雜誌 (2015-02)"/>{{rp|60}}，[[傑克·奧康奈爾_(演員)|傑克·歐康納]]<ref name="EgertonCast"/>、[[約翰·波耶加|約翰·波耶加]]<ref name="EgertonCast"/>與[[克里斯蒂安·庫克|克里斯蒂安·庫克]]等人的試鏡消息也曾被報導<ref name="EgertonCast"/><ref>{{Cite web |title=Who Will Team Up With Colin Firth in Matthew Vaughn’s ‘Secret Service’? |url=https://variety.com/2013/film/news/who-will-team-up-with-colin-firth-in-matthew-vaughns-secret-service-1200502678/ |access-date=2022-05-06 |date=2013-06-27 |last=Kroll |first=Justin |work=Variety |language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Chitwood |first=Adam |title=THE SECRET SERVICE Lead Down to Jack O’Connell, John Boyega, and Christian Cooke |url=https://collider.com/secret-service-jack-oconnell-john-boyega-christian-cooke/ |access-date=2022-05-06 |date=2013-06-27 |work=Collider |language=en-US}}</ref>。在漫畫中，這個角色的姓為倫敦（{{lang|en|London}}），是傑克·倫敦（{{lang|en|Jack London}}，即電影版中的哈利）的姪子<ref name="EW">{{cite news |last=Rivera |first=Joshua |url=https://ew.com/article/2015/02/15/kingsman-5-biggest-changes-comic-book-screen/ |title='Kingsman': 5 biggest changes from comic book to screen |work=''[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]'' |date=2015-02-15 |accessdate=2018-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180221150220/http://ew.com/article/2015/02/15/kingsman-5-biggest-changes-comic-book-screen/ |archive-date=2018-02-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

