//web.archive.org/web/20131013105758/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a487056/leonardo-dicaprio-in-talks-for-mark-millars-secret-service.html|archive-date=2013-10-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>，范恩於電影上映後表示，由狄卡皮歐來演的可能性之低就好比「我當上了教皇」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Taylor|first1=Drew|title=Matthew Vaughn Says the 'Kingsman' Sequel Will Introduce the American Branch (EXCLUSIVE)|url=http://news.moviefone.com/2015/02/11/matthew-vaughn-kingsman-interview/|website=Moviefone|date=2015-02-11|accessdate=2015-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908002335/http://news.moviefone.com/2015/02/11/matthew-vaughn-kingsman-interview/|archive-date=2015-09-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

