oved-sweet-honey-residents/|archive-date=2015-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。英國[[大倫敦|倫敦]][[五月墟市|五月墟市]]以定製服裝聞名的[[薩佛街|薩佛街]]也被用作取景地，金士曼的外裝潢及店面內裝即是以薩佛街11號的{{link-en|賀茲曼裁縫店|H. Huntsman & Sons}}為原型<ref>{{Cite web |title=Kingsman |url=https://www.savilerowbespoke.com/2015/02/kingsman/ |access-date=2022-05-06 |date=2015-02-02 |work=Savile Row Bespoke |language=en-US}}</ref>。范恩曾去這家店訂製西裝，該店的衣服也在片中出現。帽子則由{{link-en|聖詹姆士街|St James's Street}}的{{link-en|詹姆斯洛克有限公司|James Lock & Co.}}提供<ref name="DVD (Panel to Screen)"/><ref>{{cite web|title=The US love of bespoke British suits|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/av/world-us-canada-33316993/the-us-love-of-bespoke-british-suits|accessdate=2018-10-27|work=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2015-01-30|author=O'Brien, Jane|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171220233021/http://www.bbc.com/news/av/world-us-canada-33316993/the-us-love-of-bespoke-british-suits|archive-date=2017-12-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他拍攝地點包含英格蘭的{{link-en|松林製片廠|Pinewood Studios}}<ref>
