{{cite news |last=Frost |first=Caroline |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2015/01/26/kingsman-the-secret-service-taron-egerton-interview_n_6547528.html?guccounter=1&guce_referrer_us=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&guce_referrer_cs=QEgdC5i_69q7bXIRFdCpZw |title='Kingsman: The Secret Service' Star Taron Egerton Reveals What Makes Colin Firth His Coolest Co-Star |work=''[[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]]'' |date=2015-01-26 |accessdate=2018-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103001537/https://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2015/01/26/kingsman-the-secret-service-taron-egerton-interview_n_6547528.html?guccounter=1&guce_referrer_us=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&guce_referrer_cs=QEgdC5i_69q7bXIRFdCpZw |archive-date=2018-11-03 |dead-url=no }}
</ref><ref name="Hype"/>。他花了數個小時拍攝該橋段，並表示「一分鐘的水下場景得花上劇組將近10天來拍，而且我還沒有呼吸管，這是我做過最艱難的工作。」<ref name="I Look 電影雜誌 (2015-02)"/>{{rp|60}}<ref name="The Huffington Post"/>[[蘇菲·庫克森|蘇菲·庫克森]]（飾演蘿西）也親自拍了高難度的戲份<ref name="I Look 電影雜誌 (2015-02)"/>{{rp|60}}。[[蘇菲亞·波提拉|蘇菲亞·波提拉]]（飾演刀腿女葛希兒）在拍戲時腳的部分必須穿著特效用裝備，好讓劇組在後製過程中用電腦特效賦予葛希兒一雙刀腿<ref name="DVD (Panel to Screen)"/>。

